text: Karel Svoboda was a male Czech international table tennis player. He won a bronze medal at the 1931 World Table Tennis Championships in the men's doubles with Jindřich Lauterbach. He also won four consecutive team event silver medals from 1931 to 1935. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:Czech male table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
title: Karel Svoboda (table tennis)
